Barwa Bank to Sell Sukuk in 2013 After Credit Rating, CEO Says

-- B y   A m i r   S h a b a n a
-- 
2011-10-10T10:42:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/barwa-bank-to-sell-sukuk-in-2013-after-credit-rating-ceo-says.html
Barwa Bank, a unit of  Barwa Real
Estate Co. (BRES) , plans to sell Islamic bonds in 2013 after the lender
gets a  credit rating , Chief Executive Officer Steve Troop said.  The size of the sukuk will be determined in line with
market conditions at the time of the sale, he said in an
interview in Doha today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Amir Ibrahim Ali Shabana in Dubai at 
 ashabana@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Inal Ersan at 
 iersan@bloomberg.net  